node.accessibility_caption: Photo by R. M. Drake on September 01, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'I know you're strong but you have to let yourself be loved. Not everyone is going to hurt you. And not everyone is going to do you the way they did. Cause I know you're tired I can see it in your eyes. But you have to start somewhere. It's okay to try some sugar even if all your life you've been given salt. You just have to learn the difference between the two. Learn the difference between those who want nothing with you and those who genuinely care. Stay strong. -r. m. drake'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by R. M. Drake on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Everything has its place, my love. So there's no need to rush through everything. There's no need to feel as if you're going to be left behind. As if you're going to miss something important in your life. All of your moments will happen. Both the good and the bad. Because they must. And they will when you're ready. Trust your process. Trust everything the universe has aligned for you. Always. -. m. drake'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by R. M. Drake on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The way to love someone is to be honest with them. To be real. To be soft but firm when needed to. This is the way you love someone. Just say what you feel. And don't be afraid of being vulnerable with them. Don't be afraid of taking the risk. And don't be afraid of getting your heart broken. Love is a beautiful thing A miraculous thing. So be yourself. That's all it'll take to make the relationship work. -. m. drake'.
